snippet.title: Dragon Age II - The Exiled Prince
snippet.description:
Learn more about Sebastien Vael, a companion character in Dragon Age II. 

The Exiled Prince is available to those who pre-order the BioWare Signature Edition for free.

Pre-Order: http://bit.ly/hj1YTO

More Info: http://bit.ly/hLOhcA
